---
---

<section id="about" class="py-28 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-purple-400 font-medium text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Person Behind the Work</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">About</h2>
      <div class="h-px w-16 bg-purple-700 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-14">
      <!-- Headshot -->
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-700/50 to-transparent blur-sm"></div>
          <img
            src="/img/anthony_headshot.jpeg"
            alt="Anthony Owens"
            class="relative w-48 h-48 lg:w-60 lg:h-60 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-purple-700/40"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3 mt-1">
          <a
            href="https://github.com/tonedefdev"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-colors"
            aria-label="GitHub"
          >
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.746 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/anthony-owens/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-colors"
            aria-label="LinkedIn"
          >
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio -->
      <div class="text-center lg:text-left space-y-5 max-w-2xl">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Anthony Owens</h3>
          <p class="text-purple-400 text-sm font-medium mt-1">Founder, DefDev LLC &nbsp;·&nbsp; Cloud & IaC Engineer &nbsp;·&nbsp; AI/ML Practitioner &nbsp;·&nbsp; Open Source Builder</p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          Anthony possesses nearly twenty years of experience in technology — supporting businesses ranging from
          small MSPs to large hotel chains and major financial institutions like RBC in effectively integrating
          cloud technology into their operations.
        </p>

        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          He founded <span class="text-purple-400 font-medium">DefDev</span> to help emerging and established
          organizations navigate the ever-evolving technology landscape, with a focus on Cloud First, Code First
          engineering and exceptional mentorship.
        </p>

        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          Anthony actively builds and ships open source tooling for the cloud-native ecosystem — including
          <span class="text-purple-400 font-medium">OpenDepot</span>, a Kubernetes-native self-hosted registry
          for OpenTofu and Terraform modules and providers; <span class="text-purple-400 font-medium">ferme</span>,
          an end-to-end MLOps pipeline that ingests and scores the OpenTofu Registry at scale, curates fine-tuning
          datasets using a teacher LLM, and trains security-aware IaC code models via QLoRA; and
          <span class="text-purple-400 font-medium">terracreds</span>, a credential helper for securely managing
          Terraform and OpenTofu secrets.
        </p>

        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          His recent engineering focus spans <span class="text-purple-400 font-medium">Agentic AI</span> workflows,
          large-scale data ingestion pipelines, and fine-tuning open-weight language models for domain-specific
          tasks — bringing the same infrastructure-first discipline he applies to cloud engineering directly into
          the ML stack.
        </p>

        <a
          href="#projects"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 text-sm font-medium transition-colors"
        >
          View my projects
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
